    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="0f074733-e296-4bf4-8953-f6a32a03bd12">
      <Text>I miss you too. I'm coming in like</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Type="Dialogue" id="8d761d45-0ea0-475d-8571-3f448d468fed">
      <Text>2 weeks. Guess what? My friend got a tattoo on her pussy.</Text>
